                                                                                                                                Data and tables

                                                                                                                                Charts

                                                                                                                                Charts is a global library for data visualization that provides reusable, flexible chart modules that can be used across all platforms and lines of business.

                                                                                                                                Usage
                                                                                                                                Charts by concepts
                                                                                                                                Chart colors
                                                                                                                                Base charts library

                                                                                                                                Turn on the Base charts team library to get started.

                                                                                                                                Module overview

                                                                                                                                Each chart is made up of a sum of parts, each part being its own individual module that is swappable for maximum customizability. You can also build your own custom charts by snapping these parts together—more on that later.

                                                                                                                                Flexible modules

                                                                                                                                Every module is 100% flexible! This means no matter what kind of space your tool has, the chart will fit and will not result in a wonky design—no more forced detaching. As you scale these modules, each part will stay in its place and will scale appropriately.


                                                                                                                                Don’t
                                                                                                                                Do not let the labels overlap each other
                                                                                                                                Do
                                                                                                                                Ensure there is enough room for the labels
                                                                                                                                Do
                                                                                                                                Surface the labels when interacting with the chart

                                                                                                                                Colors

                                                                                                                                We're excited about our color palette, specially crafted for data visualization. You can visit the color page for more information about visualization color standards. For ease, we have organized them by primary and secondary qualitative colors and have separated the scales into their respective categories (single-hue, multi-hue, and divergent).

                                                                                                                                Build a chart

                                                                                                                                For building your own chart or swapping instances of an atomic part, you can either search for the specific part you're looking for or find it in the module structure panel (below)

                                                                                                                                Search for a chart

                                                                                                                                Chart Type -> Chart Variation(s) -> Legend

                                                                                                                                Drag any template from the Library

                                                                                                                                We offer many different variations of grids—dotted grids, flushed grids and more. We can't make a permutation for every chart. So we created grid modules where you can swap out the placeholders with your graph! Just drag them from the library or copy and paste your desired grid from the templates page and go!

                                                                                                                                Select the placeholder

                                                                                                                                Swap it with any visualization

                                                                                                                                That's it! You're done!
